Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:02.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There, they've rounded the final corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We're down to the last 200 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Which horse will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:07.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Will it be the favorite, Iron Blade, in Lane 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe even the trump in lane 2, Devil Typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The outcome will depend on the fighting spirit of each horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the Mouri Detective Agency's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clue is a large scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Differentiate between the first love and the suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Iron Blade in Lane 4 leads by a half-length...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Masked Yaiba in Lane isn't far behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And Black Chaser in Lane 8 is close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We have one coming from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Devil Typhoon! Devil Typhoon! It's Devil Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:27.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The winner is Devil Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected outcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The crowd is in an uproar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three million jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching over this detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially during this particularly difficult month!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because we practically had no cases this month...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The judge's deliberation lamp has been lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Was there a problem in the scramble to the finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Devil Typhoon in Lane 2 has been disqualified for stepping out of lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And now, the new order has the winner as Iron Blade from Lane 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you always been on my side, buddy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a rich lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who bought a lottery ticket on a whim and won 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all over the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she said she plans to give the winning ticket to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that, when she met with a traffic accident in her childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boy was seriously injured trying to protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she wanted to express her gratitude by giving\Nhim the 100 million, if he would come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has this lucky boy appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the course of the accident, her eyes\Nwere damaged and she lost her sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the boy was also a child then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't be able to identify him by his face or voice anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does she intend to find that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the injury he sustained during the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a huge wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even after growing into an adult, the scar would still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, I have a scar as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago —\hit's the scar from when I slid headfirst\Non the baseball field and injured the top of my shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think there's any chance I can fake it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Fake it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, this old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a straight tear across his T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I clearly recall the blood seeping from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, my eyesight began to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the only image I cannot forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this person—the 100 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, are you here to ask me to find\Nthat boy by using only the scar as a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are people who have come forward claiming they are the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd like for me to determine which of these two is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.92,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shoudou Kurumi (39)\NHead of the Shoudou Family
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The boy who saved me was just one person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who would pretend to be the one from\Nthis kind lady's memory for the sake of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shameless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you observe the scars on the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Houya Taisuke (40)\NButler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Although I did see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brown-haired man has it on his back, while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with the dark complexion has one on his chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them have very large scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the back and chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, do you not know the location of the wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only remember that it was severe and nearly went from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where did the accident occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the summer holidays, some thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened while I was on vacation with my parents in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met a boy around my age at the beach, and we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the vacation, we played together every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was very familiar with the sea and the types of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he always drank ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked so cute when I could see his white teeth\Ngleaming alongside his tanned face from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, those dream-like days couldn't last for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the last day of the vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I cried and told him, "I don't want to go home..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Then, stay here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll protect you," is what he said at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how old were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I was in my second year of elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lovey-dovey even in the second year of elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how did the accident happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I selfishly petitioned for my parents to stay in Izu for one more day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw him walking on the road near\Nthe coastline, I tried to run up and tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just when I caught him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A drowsy driver ended up veering toward the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, I was unconscious for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was already in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know what became of that boy after that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told later that that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had carried me to the hospital with a large wound of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told the hospital staff that he would call for his parents and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But was never seen there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have asked for his name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, you had been playing together for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My classmates refer to me as Gari, so\Nthat's what you can call me as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the answer you gave on TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gari" should be able to count as a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are those two who came forward right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been staying at my house for the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a luxurious home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet a place this big sure takes a while to get clean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all due to the limitless effort of Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the two maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since there are only four of us living here, including myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are rarely many places that need cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I bet the dusting is more than enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say "four" people, does that mean your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother passed away from illness some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father, who had taken care of me until his\Ndeath, fell ill and passed on three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just prior to my father's passing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to hire this butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the one who took on the burden of caring for me, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly no burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems we've added two more recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, with you, that will bring us to nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose we'll have quite a feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So good, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As they say, the more the merrier when meals are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of us here doesn't belong, and yet is getting a free meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0}Kasumoto Ryuuhei (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's best if you admit it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Impostor{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0}Banba Sougo (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I think I'm the one who should be saying just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll sort this out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri will ascertain the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that not so, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll question them in the next room, individually, for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Detective{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do your best to differentiate between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The possibility remains that both of them are impostors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it has been thirty years now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible the boy has already passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that he is in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse to think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I specially requested the great\Ndetective, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that I've grown a little tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll retreat to my room for some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you have reached your conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come and reveal it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already know which one is him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see something outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if we were being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not really feeling anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle inquired with the two of them\Nover the boy from thirty years ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of them only repeated the same answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that was to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She mentioned everything about the situation in her TV interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The date of the accident, the model of the car, and\Neven the name of the facility she was hospitalized in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would explain why they answered\Nall the questions exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I identify which is which, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, there is someone out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's not just one or two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are we doing outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, and Detective Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're on a stakeout...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the suspect from fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one who left this scar on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} had just been promoted to detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wasn't involved in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I was assigned to the metropolitan\Npolice, I'm pretty sure you already had that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five years prior to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That same suspect gave me this scar with a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cornered him at the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took the katana from his hand and paid him a strike of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a 1-shaped scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1-shaped scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing this woman's story on the news a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured that guy would take notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the scar from the katana on his chest or his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't quite remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was certainly a worthy adversary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at the time, the superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had just been cut across his left eye, so it wasn't easy for him to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems I was right in coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This scar on my left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's telling me that our man is in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a serial killer from fifteen years ago is in this house!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still aren't sure if he's actually in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said earlier about us being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto has been\Nlooking for this criminal for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems this was the one who gave him the scar on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at the same time, the superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used that guy's katana in retaliation\Nand left a 1-shaped wound on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1-shaped wound—does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem the serial killer has it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one side to the other, there should\Nbe a large wound from the katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why has a serial killer come to this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely he has his sights set on the 100 million yen lottery ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he can use the scar he got from the superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy from her memories could be either the brown-\Nhaired Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} or the dark-skinned Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one that isn't could be the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the serial killer's scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s scar is on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s is on his chest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the superintendent doesn't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it did happen just after his eye was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you mean to say there aren't\Nany other clues aside from the scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the culprit then was wearing gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which meant they couldn't lift any fingerprints\Nfrom the katana that was taken from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since the katana had been the\Nmurder weapon in multiple cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood of the criminal and that of his victims had\Nmixed together, which made it difficult to pinpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't see his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a hat, long hair, and beard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was clearly a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's obviously not going to be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the murderer was always whistling a certain melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto said, "Casually keep\Nwatch over those two and find out who is who."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what kind of melody is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reluctant to share any further information\Nwith me, and when I tried to get it out of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it's possible that I would make it "obvious" a\Npolice investigation was ongoing, so he didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's such a dangerous person in here, there's\Nno reason to have sent Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually had no choice but to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I suddenly disappeared, the murderer might suspect something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then discover the police watching over the house outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't be 100% sure that one of those two is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bath has been prepared, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Offering a bath, even after treating us to that feast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you would be so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's only one washroom here, so should you wish to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the young lady should go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to use a washroom at\Na place like this for a long time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go in together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we washed each other's backs, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any clothes to change into...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was just in one yesterday, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really want to do it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you probably wouldn't want\Nto go, so I decided not to enter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can focus on the murderer instead of the bath now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, so long as we don't know which melody he\Nwhistled so often, there isn't much to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll need to see through those two\Nand find out which is the boy from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro talked with Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They mentioned the day of the accident and\Nthe name of the hospital she was taken to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they both relayed the same story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were they really identical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even a small difference between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were there and didn't listen this one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blame the police outside for getting my attention instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only their stories differed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} claimed he was was thin as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said he was always studying hard when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to ask that lady yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already knows exactly which one is the one she's looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen these in dramas and movies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think this sort of luxurious bath exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd join you if you didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two entering together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be well acquainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you were coming into the bath, so I thought I'd join you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And maybe see how your case is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already know which of us is real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trade secret, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I can ask about the melody just as the superintendent\Nrequested, but without approaching these two directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that the butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You joining us as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am only here to see to the detective's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per request of the madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, I believe you're suspecting too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had already known which it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would have had no reason for calling Detective Mouri here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything from the past you omitted during the TV interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I believe I included it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, he was a perfectly honest person by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be simple for Detective Mouri to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfectly honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He bought packed sushi for lunch, and when he later\Nrealized he'd received 100 extra yen in change...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went really far out of his way to return it to the shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it was because it didn't belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person liked sushi, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:20:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we ate fried noodles in a house by the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to see him heap such a\Nlarge amount of red ginger onto his plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be the first time I've heard that story...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, please relay that to Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, please do not bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I enter a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like reciting "Hana Uta," or another great tune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happen to have any favorite songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a melody I find myself humming a lot, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've received a mail from Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The brown-haired guy chooses jazz...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"While the dark-skinned guy prefers soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return a mail to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Continue the investigation," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To order me around just when I send news...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Butler, you doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a pretty heavy sweat going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air conditioning in the bathroom went out not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the sweat, I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of people with a 1-shaped scar in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is now up to a total of three...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wondering whether it's natural or manufactured?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter on the bodies of the victims, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:35.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Order any sushi you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.99,0:24:38.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,All righty, let's have sea urchin,\Nabalone, tuna belly, salmon roe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, two eggs.
